                "text": {
                  "status": "generated",
                  "div": "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><h3>Microbiology</h3><table class=\"hl7__eu__lab__report\"><thead><tr><th>Test</th><th>02-FEB-2021</th><th>Reference&#xA0;Range</th><th>Unit</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Influenza virus A RNA [Presence] in Respiratory system specimen by NAA with probe detection</td><td>Negative</td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td>Influenza virus B RNA [Presence] in Respiratory system specimen by NAA with probe detection</td><td>Negative</td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td>Respiratory syncytial virus RNA [Presence] in Respiratory system specimen by NAA with probe detection</td><td>Negative</td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td>Parainfluenza virus 1 RNA [Presence] in Respiratory system specimen by NAA with probe detection</td><td>Negative</td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td>Parainfluenza virus 2 RNA [Presence] in Respiratory system specimen by NAA with probe detection</td><td>Negative</td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td>Parainfluenza virus 3 RNA [Presence] in Respiratory system specimen by NAA with probe detection</td><td>Negative</td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td>Rhinovirus RNA [Presence] in Respiratory system specimen by NAA with probe detection</td><td>Negative</td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td>Human metapneumovirus RNA [Presence] in Respiratory system specimen by NAA with probe detection</td><td>Negative</td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td>Adenovirus A+B+C+D+E DNA [Presence] in Respiratory system specimen by NAA with probe detection</td><td>Negative</td><td></td><td></td></tr></tbody></table></div>"
