          {
            "text": {
              "status": "generated",
              "div": "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><h3>Annotation</h3><table class=\"hl7__eu__lab__report\"><tr><th>Conclusion and Recommendations based on this report and previous findings known to us</th></tr><tr><td>All tested respiratory viruses (influenza A/B, RSV, parainfluenza 1-3, rhinovirus, human metapneumovirus, adenovirus) were not detected in the respiratory specimen. These results suggest no evidence of acute infection with these common respiratory viruses at the time of sampling.</td></tr></table></div>"
